                <mxCell id="5" value="&lt;blockquote data-end=&quot;87&quot; data-start=&quot;14&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-end=&quot;87&quot; data-start=&quot;16&quot;&gt;“What happens when a &lt;strong data-end=&quot;85&quot; data-start=&quot;37&quot;&gt;Client Component contains a Server Component&lt;/strong&gt;?”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;p data-end=&quot;147&quot; data-start=&quot;89&quot;&gt;👉 That is &lt;strong data-end=&quot;124&quot; data-start=&quot;100&quot;&gt;NOT allowed directly&lt;/strong&gt; in Next.js App Router&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-end=&quot;147&quot; data-start=&quot;89&quot;&gt;After hydration, browser cannot suddenly execute server-only code.&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=default;fillColor=none;" parent="1" vertex="1">
