                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="27" value="&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;CON: - used for dynamic page that are frequently or most visited&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;PON: - if the dynamic data change frequently, then it will not be shown untill we rebuild site&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;strokeColor=default;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=4;spacingRight=4;overflow=hidden;points=[[0,0.5],[1,0.5]];portConstraint=eastwest;rotatable=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;dashed=1;dashPattern=1 4;" parent="22" vertex="1">
